reviewText:
I Love the savings here. I think all 3 movies are damn good.
Yeah I've heard the jokes.."What's Happening?"  But I liked it.
Jumper has Anakin Skywalker in it...and he's good, in several of his recent movies.
Jake is just a master of his craft. He's amazing.
Love getting these multi-movie packs and this is a good one with 3 good movies.
